MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2001-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 16th March, 2001.
25 Phalguna, 1922(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 16th March,
2001:-
i)
Shri George Fernandes relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
Defence;
ii)
Ms. Mamata Banerjee relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
Railways;
iii)
Shri Ajit Kumar Panja relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Ministry of External Affairs; and
iv)
the Prime Minister assumed the charge of the offices of Minister of
Defence and Minister of Railways.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 3015802
